Look at the environment that we're talking about here. We are talking about Everquest. How many people have KSed,trained,or harrassed you and never apologize? Or apologize and do it again rather, and try a &quot;oops im sorry&quot; to try to get you off their back? Or go &quot;hehe i'm sorry i dint no u were kiting it hehe it didnt look snared hun hehe&quot;? *grits teeth bitterly*.<br>
