To put it in a nutshell, you can hide in EQ. You CAN make an alternate character. You CAN put people on /ignore. You CAN just /burp rudely in the faces of the people that are mad at you and still get a group when you want it.<br>
<br>
Don't assume he's just apologizing to get everyone off his back.<br>
Don't assume he just got a soul transplant,has angels dancing around him and has daisies singing his praises either.<br>
<br>
I wouldn't expect it if I did the same things either. <p><center>
